551
00:36:20,595 --> 00:36:22,180
Go back to the list?

552
00:36:22,263 --> 00:36:25,016
He was fine, but I'm not enthused
by anyone else on that list.

553
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:27,518
Let's not go back to square one,
Mr. President.

554
00:36:27,602 --> 00:36:29,145
We have a good list.

555
00:36:29,229 --> 00:36:30,646
