We'll own the news.

584
00:37:59,277 --> 00:38:01,321
You want the convention to be a circus.

585
00:38:01,404 --> 00:38:03,949
Oh, Bob, I'm not sure
if you've noticed or not,

586
00:38:04,032 --> 00:38:07,702
but politics is no longer just theater,
it's show business.

587
00:38:07,786 --> 00:38:10,330
So let's put on the best show in town.

588
00:38:11,164 --> 00:38:12,457
Great.

589
00:38:12,540 --> 00:38:14,167
Will you give me a salute, General?

590
00:38:19,297 --> 00:38:21,716
Active military aren't allowed
to speak to the press.

591
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:24,302
He delivered his resignation this morning.

592
00:38:24,385 --> 00:38:25,678
No shit.

593
00:38:25,761 --> 00:38:28,890
We're gonna break it online
as soon as the president accepts it.

594
00:38:29,599 --> 00:38:32,310
